Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors

Classes implementing the Visitor pattern used to perform various functions on the activity definitions.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeDefMessagePartsMapVisitor visits each node and inlines the message parts info used for the wsio operation
IAeDefPathSegmentVisitor A non-traversing visitor (double-dispatch only) that produces the appropriate value for a def's segment path.
IAeDefPathVisitor Defines a def path visitor.
IAeDefToImplVisitor interface for the def to impl visitor
IAeDefTraverser Traversal interface for use in conjunction with BPEL definition object visitation.
IAeDefVisitor Visitor interface for BPEL Definition classes.
IAeDefVisitorFactory Factory for the def visitors that have different implementations depending on the version of BPEL we're dealing with
 

Class Summary
AeAbstractDefMessagePartsMapVisitor Base visitor that visits each wsio activity and inlines the message parts data for the message being sent or received.
AeAbstractDefPathSegmentVisitor Non-traversing visitor that gets the path to use for a def or null if the def doesn't have a location path.
AeAbstractDefVisitor A base class for other visitors.
AeAbstractEntryPointVisitor Abstract visitor for visiting entry point def objects in an AeProcessDef object.
AeAbstractExpressionDefVisitor An abstract visitor that visits all expression defs.
AeAbstractSearchVisitor Base class for visitors that are searching for a particular def and want to stop traversing after its found.
AeBPWSDefMessagePartsMapVisitor Visits each of the wsio activities and inlines the message part information.
AeBPWSDefPathSegmentVisitor A def path visitor implementation for BPEL4WS 1.1
AeBPWSDefVisitorFactory Factory for creating def visitors for BPEL4WS 1.1 defs
AeBPWSMessageExchangeDefPathSegmentVisitor A def path visitor extension for BPEL4WS 1.1 which also assigns paths for message exchanges.
AeBPWSScopeTerminationStrategy Strategy used to terminate an executing scope for BPEL4WS 1.1.
AeCheckStartActivityVisitor Class which implements a visitor pattern used to validate that the current process conforms to the BPEL constraint regarding Create Instance usage.
AeChildScopeByNameVisitor Visitor that locates a child scope by name.
AeChildScopesVisitor Visitor that locates child scopes.
AeCopyOperationStrategyVisitor Visits the process def and adds the strategy hint to the copy operation defs: and .
AeCreateInstanceMessageExchangeVisitor Records the messageExchange attribute for all of the createInstance activities.
AeCreateInstanceOperationVisitor Walks the process def looking to see if the createInstance operation is used by more than one IMA.
AeCreateInstanceVisitor  
AeDefAssignParentVisitor Visitor responsible for assigning parent-to-child relationships among the def model.
AeDefCorrelatedReceiveVisitor This visitor walks the process def collecting information about correlated receives.
AeDefCreateInvokeScopeVisitor A def visitor that will find any Invokes that have implicit scopes and make those scopes explicit in the Def tree.
AeDefEntryPointInitialVisitor Builds a list of keys (partnerLinkName:PortQName:operationName) for initial entry points into the BPEL process.
AeDefEntryPointPropertiesVisitor Visit all of the receives and picks and build a mapping of partnerLinkName:portTypeQName:operationName to a set of correlation properties.
AeDefExtensionFinderVisitor This visitor will look for extension elements/attributes.
AeDefFindVisitor Visitor to find a definition given a specific path.
AeDefInlineInvokeScopeVisitor This is the foil to the AeDefCreateInvokeScopeVisitor class.
AeDefNullPathVisitor Visitor responsible for creating location paths for process definition objects which do not already have location paths assigned.
AeDefOnEventVariableTypeVisitor Assigns variable types to implicit variables created for onEvent fromPart variable references by AeWSBPELImplicitVariableVisitor.
AeDefOneWayVisitor This visitor traverses the tree looking for receives and on-message object.
AeDefPartnerLinkNameVisitor This visitor is responsible for visiting all of the partner links and adding mappings for them in the process def.
AeDefPartnerLinkTypeVisitor Sets the IAePartnerLinkType reference on each of the partner link def objects.
AeDefPathParallelVisitor Extension of the location path visitor that creates a custom path for the root scope of the forEach.
AeDefPathVisitor Visitor responsible for creating location paths for process definition objects.
AeDefToBPWSImplVisitor Creates impl objects for BPEL4WS 1.1
AeDefToImplVisitor Visitor responsible for creating implementation objects from their definition objects.
AeDefToWSBPELImplVisitor Creates impl objects for WS-BPEL 2.0
AeDefTraverser The external iterator for the IAeDefVisitor interface.
AeDefVariableTypeVisitor Visitor that sets the Part and Type data for each variable.
AeDefVariableUsageVisitor Visitor that compiles a set of variables used for each activity.
AeDefVariableUsageVisitor.AeLockType An enumerated constant for read locks and write locks, not used outside of this class.
AeDefVisitorFactory Factory for creating def visitors
AeDoXslTransformUriVisitor Visits the process def and builds a list of doXslTransform() resources.
AeImplementationTraverser Customized traverser that skips over the child scope for parallel forEach activities.
AeImplicitVariableVisitor A visitor responsible for creating implicit variables on def objects.
AeInlinePropertyAliasVisitor Visits the def to inline usage of property alias's where possible.
AeIsolatedScopeVisitor Visitor that sets AeActivityDef.setIsolatedScope(AeActivityScopeDef) for all activities.
AeJoinVisitor Visits each correlation and records whether the correlation is an initiate="yes" on the correlationSet.
AeJoinVisitor.AeCorrelationSetUsage simple struct for maintaining the usage info for a correlationSet.
AeMessageExchangeVisitor Records the messageExchange attribute for all of the createInstance activities.
AePartnerLinkValidationVisitor Visitor used to determine if a partner link name is being used in an invoke.
AeScopeSnapshotOptimizationVisitor Visits the scopes to determine which scopes need to record snapshots when they complete due to a nested explicit compensation handler's access to variables, correlationSets, partnerLinks.
AeTraversalVisitor A specialized visitor that takes another visitor and a traversal object and calls the appropriate traverse method during each visitation.
AeWSBPELAbstractProcessDefVisitorFactory Factory for creating def visitors for WS-BPEL 2.0 abstract process defs.
AeWSBPELDefMessagePartsMapVisitor Assigns AeMessagePartsMap info to web service activities.
AeWSBPELDefPathSegmentVisitor No behavior here for this class.
AeWSBPELDefVariableUsageVisitor Def visitor that records resources that need to be locked for WS-BPEL 2.0 rules.
AeWSBPELDefVisitorFactory Factory for creating def visitors for WS-BPEL 2.0 defs
AeWSBPELImplementationTraverser WS-BPEL 2.0 traverser
AeWSBPELImplicitVariableVisitor Adds the implicit variable declaration where needed in 2.0
AeWSBPELInlinePropertyAliasVisitor Provides WS-BPEL 2.0 logic for inlining propertyAliases
AeWSBPELMessageExchangeVisitor Adds support for the onEvent's child scope as a root scope
AeWSBPELScopeTerminationStrategy Strategy used to terminate an executing scope for WS-BPEL 2.0.
